```

## Testing Checklist

Before deploying changes:

- [ ] All links work (especially signup CTAs)
- [ ] Mobile responsive (test at 375px width)
- [ ] No console errors
- [ ] UTM tracking fires correctly (check Network tab)
- [ ] Calendly popup works
- [ ] Images load correctly
- [ ] Text is readable (contrast, size)

## Performance

- Optimize images before adding (compress, appropriate dimensions)
- Lazy load images below the fold where possible
- Keep JavaScript minimal and non-blocking
- Avoid large third-party dependencies

## Accessibility

- Maintain keyboard navigation for interactive elements
- Use sufficient color contrast (WCAG AA minimum)
- Include `aria-hidden="true"` on decorative elements
- Ensure focus states are visible on interactive elements

